<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how-it-works" class="section hiw-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="slabel">The Experience</div>
    <h2>One Booking. Zero Stress. <span class="grad">A Day They Won't Stop Talking About.</span></h2>
    <p class="sdesc">You show up. We handle everything else — the bus, the venue, the food, the fun.</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="sn">01</div>
        <img src="/images/Party Bus Kids.jpg" alt="Kids boarding party bus Las Vegas" loading="lazy"/>
        <h3>Meet &amp; Board the Bus</h3>
        <p>Check in at APEX BJJ, grab your wristband, and climb aboard. Music's already pumping before we leave the lot.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sarr">→</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="sn">02</div>
        <img src="/images/Party Bus Kids-013.jpg" alt="Kids dancing on party bus" loading="lazy"/>
        <h3>Party Bus Cruise</h3>
        <p>1 hour of pure energy — dancing, games, glow accessories, juice &amp; sodas. The ride is half the party.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sarr">→</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="sn">03</div>
        <img src="/images/Party Bus Kids-115.jpg" alt="Kids at venue Las Vegas" loading="lazy"/>
        <h3>Your Chosen Adventure</h3>
        <p>Sky Zone, Dave &amp; Buster's, or Area 15 — 1 hour of dedicated action with everything pre-arranged. No lines, no hassle.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sarr">→</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="sn">04</div>
        <img src="/images/Party Bus Kids-107.jpg" alt="Kids pizza party celebration" loading="lazy"/>
        <h3>Private Pizza Party</h3>
        <p>Reserved room, hot pizza, drinks, and a party host. Bring a cake — we'll make it a moment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

