<!-- INCLUSIONS -->
<section id="included" class="section inc-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="slabel">All-Inclusive</div>
    <h2>Everything Included. <span class="grad">Zero Surprises.</span></h2>
    <p class="sdesc">Other party companies charge extra for wristbands, food, and gratuity. We bundle everything so the price you book is the price you pay.</p>
    <div class="inc-grid">
      <div class="inc"><div class="ii">🚌</div><h4>VIP Party Bus</h4><p>Professional driver, music, glow accessories, and beverages. The ride is half the party.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="ii">🎵</div><h4>Their Playlist</h4><p>Bluetooth audio on the bus — whatever gets the group hyped. DJ, pop, hip-hop, whatever they want.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="ii">🥤</div><h4>Juices &amp; Sodas</h4><p>Chilled juices, water, and sodas stocked on the bus and at the pizza party. No upcharges.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="ii">🎯</div><h4>Venue Admission</h4><p>Sky Zone jump time, D&amp;B game credits, or Area 15 entry — fully pre-arranged and paid. Just walk in.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="ii">🍕</div><h4>Private Pizza Party</h4><p>Reserved room, hot pizza, drinks, and a dedicated party host. Bring a cake — we'll handle the moment.</p></div>
      <div class="inc"><div class="ii">💰</div><h4>All Gratuity Included</h4><p>Driver tip and host gratuity are both built in. No awkward math or surprise charges at the end.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="inc-photos">
