    <h2>Questions <span class="grad">Parents Ask</span></h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>What ages is this for?</summary><p>Designed for kids and teens ages 6–16. Activities and venues are matched to the group. Mixed-age group? Contact us and we'll make sure the day works for everyone.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>Can I choose which venue we go to?</summary><p>Yes — that's the whole point. Pick Sky Zone for a trampolining crew, Dave &amp; Buster's for arcade lovers, or Area 15 for a more immersive experience. If you have something else in mind, reach out and we'll see what we can arrange.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>Do I have to come along as a parent?</summary><p>You're always welcome, and one parent rides free for every 5 kids. Many parents use the 3.5 hours for themselves. Additional parents can join — just ask when booking.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>How do you keep the kids safe?</summary><p>Every child is checked in and wristbanded at arrival. Background-checked staff stays with the group at every stop. You get real-time updates throughout the day, and kids are only released to pre-approved adults at pickup.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>What's included in the price?</summary><p>Everything: party bus with beverages and games, venue admission (Sky Zone jump time, D&B game credits, or Area 15 entry), private pizza party with food and drinks, party host, VIP wristbands, driver gratuity, and host gratuity.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>Can we bring a birthday cake?</summary><p>Absolutely. Bring a cake (or cupcakes) to the pizza party and our host will make sure there's a proper moment. We'll handle the rest.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>What if my child has a food allergy?</summary><p>Let us know when you book. We work with you to accommodate dietary needs so every child can enjoy the pizza party safely.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>How many kids can you take?</summary><p>All sizes — from small birthday parties to large group events with 30+ kids. Vehicle scales with your group. Contact us for large group pricing.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>How far in advance should I book?</summary><p>The sooner the better. Popular dates — especially weekends and school breaks — fill up fast. You can lock in your date with just 30% down if you're booking 7+ days out.</p></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary>What's the cancellation policy?</summary><p>Cancel 7+ days out for a 70% refund. Add Trip Insurance at checkout to cancel up to 48 hours before for a full refund, or reschedule once at no charge.</p></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

